metatags.og:title: Some days feel like dreams… not reality and this interview with Judy Khan Shaw was a dream. | Rachel Zillner | 22 comments
metatags.og:description:
Some days feel like dreams… not reality and this interview with Judy Khan Shaw was a dream. It was Monday, Anne Descalzo and I had flown on a red eye and landed in America’s vibrant New York. From there it was a blur of lights and people and so much cool stuff!! I did some serious #fearboxing that day. Then was so impressed with how ease and flow the engagement was. Anne and I shared tears of elation in seeing our logo everywhere - hearts swelled with joy and pride. After the interview we had time to learn about Judy’s personal story as one of the few (at times only) women on the NYSE floor. Please take three minutes and watch our interview and follow her channel, she interviews so many cool entrepreneurs!!!

So excited to share what’s happening in City of Rancho Cordova with the addition of Clutch HQ and the new innovations on the first floor!!!
